      "code": "def lcs_length(a,b):\r\n    n,m = len(a), len(b)\r\n    dp = [0]*(m+1)\r\n    for i in range(1, n+1):\r\n        prev = 0\r\n        for j in range(1, m+1):\r\n            temp = dp[j]\r\n            if a[i-1]==b[j-1]:\r\n                dp[j] = prev+1\r\n            else:\r\n                if dp[j] < dp[j-1]:\r\n                    dp[j] = dp[j-1]\r\n            prev = temp\r\n    return dp[m]\r\n\r\nlcs = lcs_length(ns_original, ns_candidate)\r\nratio = lcs / max(len(ns_original), len(ns_candidate))\r\nlcs, ratio",
